# App capability dependencies for SDK config merge
#
# Syntax:
#   CONFIG_<SYMBOL>=y
#
# Notes:
# - Keep one symbol per line.
# - Empty lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
# - This file is merged into build-time effective.config by sdk-new CMake flow.
# - Unknown or unsupported symbols will be caught by capability checks.
#
# Example:
# CONFIG_QCM_MQTT_FUNC=y
# CONFIG_QCM_UTILS_UTILS_FUNC=y
# CONFIG_QCM_VTLS_FUNC=y
